---
layout: base.njk
title: Nuevo para ti | La Otra Pucela
description: Artículos que aún no has leído, ordenados por fecha y filtrables por temática.
ogTitle: Nuevo para ti | La Otra Pucela
ogDescription: Artículos que aún no has leído, ordenados por fecha y filtrables por temática.
canonicalUrl: /nuevo/
---
{% set sortedThemes = articulos.tags | topThemes(999) %}
<section class="mx-auto max-w-5xl px-4 py-5 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 lg:py-10">
  <div class="max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="font-serif text-[2.5rem] font-semibold leading-[0.98] tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-[3.3rem]">
      Nuevo para ti
    </h1>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-[22rem] text-[1.02rem] leading-[1.65] text-gray-600 sm:max-w-3xl" data-unread-intro>
      Aquí verás los artículos que todavía no has leído, ordenados de más reciente a más antiguo.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-7" data-unread-page>
    <div class="hidden rounded-[1.75rem] border border-gray-200 bg-white px-6 py-7 shadow-sm" data-unread-loading>
      <p class="text-base leading-[1.6] text-gray-600">Cargando artículos pendientes…</p>
    </div>

    <div class="hidden rounded-[1.75rem] border border-[#DDD7CC] bg-[#F6F1E7] px-6 py-7 shadow-sm" data-unread-empty>
      <p class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900">No tienes nada pendiente</p>
      <p class="mt-2 max-w-2xl text-base leading-[1.6] text-[#5F5645]" data-unread-empty-copy>
        Cuando publiquemos algo nuevo que aún no hayas leído, aparecerá aquí.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-6">
        <a
          href="/"
          class="inline-flex min-h-12 items-center justify-center gap-2 rounded-full bg-[#1F2937] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-white transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-[#111827]"
        >
          <i class="fa-solid fa-house text-sm" aria-hidden="true"></i>
          <span>Ir a portada</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="hidden max-w-3xl" data-unread-container>
      <div class="mb-5 border-b border-[#E7E1D6] pb-5">
        <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 lg:hidden">
          <div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-4">
            <p class="text-sm leading-[1.6] text-gray-600">
              <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900" data-unread-count>0</span>
              sin leer
            </p>

            <label class="inline-flex min-h-11 items-center gap-2 text-sm leading-[1.6] text-gray-700">
              <input
                type="checkbox"
                class="peer sr-only"
                data-unread-counter-toggle
              >
              <span class="inline-flex min-h-10 items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-[#D9D1C4] bg-white px-3 py-2 text-[#6B6253] transition-colors duration-200 peer-focus-visible:outline peer-focus-visible:outline-2 peer-focus-visible:outline-offset-2 peer-focus-visible:outline-[#D9D1C4] peer-checked:border-[#C7D8D0] peer-checked:bg-[#DCE7E1] peer-checked:text-[#31453D]">
                <i class="fa-solid fa-bell text-[0.78rem]" aria-hidden="true"></i>
                <span class="text-[0.72rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.08em]">Contador</span>
              </span>
            </label>
          </div>

          <select
            class="min-h-12 w-full rounded-full border border-[#D9D1C4] bg-white px-4 text-[0.98rem] text-gray-900 outline-none transition-colors duration-200 focus:border-gray-900 sm:w-[18rem]"
            data-unread-theme-filter
          >
            <option value="">Todas las temáticas</option>
            {% for tag in sortedThemes %}
            <option value="{{ tag.slug }}">{{ tag.name | themeName }}</option>
            {% endfor %}
          </select>
        </div>

        <div class="hidden lg:grid lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_auto] lg:gap-x-10 lg:gap-y-4 lg:items-center">
          <p class="text-sm leading-[1.6] text-gray-600">
            <span class="font-semibold text-gray-900" data-unread-count>0</span>
            sin leer
          </p>

          <label class="inline-flex min-h-11 items-center justify-self-end gap-2 text-sm leading-[1.6] text-gray-700">
            <input
              type="checkbox"
              class="peer sr-only"
              data-unread-counter-toggle
            >
            <span class="inline-flex min-h-10 items-center gap-2 rounded-full border border-[#D9D1C4] bg-white px-3 py-2 text-[#6B6253] transition-colors duration-200 peer-focus-visible:outline peer-focus-visible:outline-2 peer-focus-visible:outline-offset-2 peer-focus-visible:outline-[#D9D1C4] peer-checked:border-[#C7D8D0] peer-checked:bg-[#DCE7E1] peer-checked:text-[#31453D]">
              <i class="fa-solid fa-bell text-[0.78rem]" aria-hidden="true"></i>
              <span class="text-[0.72rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.08em]">Contador</span>
            </span>
          </label>

          <select
            class="min-h-12 w-full max-w-[18rem] rounded-full border border-[#D9D1C4] bg-white px-4 text-[0.98rem] text-gray-900 outline-none transition-colors duration-200 focus:border-gray-900"
            data-unread-theme-filter
          >
            <option value="">Todas las temáticas</option>
            {% for tag in sortedThemes %}
            <option value="{{ tag.slug }}">{{ tag.name | themeName }}</option>
            {% endfor %}
          </select>

          <button
            type="button"
            class="inline-flex min-h-10 items-center justify-center justify-self-end rounded-full border border-[#D9D1C4] bg-white px-3.5 py-2 text-[0.72rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-[#3F3424] transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-[#F3EBDD]"
            data-unread-mark-all-read
          >
            Marcar todo como leído
          </button>
        </div>

        <button
          type="button"
          class="mt-4 inline-flex min-h-11 w-full items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-[#D9D1C4] bg-white px-4 py-2.5 text-[0.76rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-[#3F3424] transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-[#F3EBDD] lg:hidden"
          data-unread-mark-all-read-mobile
        >
          Marcar todo como leído
        </button>
      </div>

      <div class="hidden rounded-[1.5rem] border border-[#E7E0D3] bg-[#FCFBF8] px-5 py-6 text-sm leading-[1.6] text-gray-600" data-unread-filter-empty>
        <p class="font-semibold text-gray-900">No hay artículos pendientes en esta temática.</p>
        <p class="mt-1">Prueba con otra o vuelve a todas.</p>
      </div>

      <div data-unread-items></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<dialog
  class="w-[min(92vw,30rem)] rounded-[2rem] border border-[#DDD7CC] bg-[#FFFDF8] p-0 text-gray-900 shadow-2xl backdrop:bg-[#2F3E46]/55"
  data-unread-confirm-dialog
  aria-labelledby="unread-confirm-title"
>
  <div class="px-5 pb-6 pt-7 sm:px-7 sm:pb-7 sm:pt-8">
    <div class="mx-auto flex h-14 w-14 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#F3EBDD] text-[#6B6253]">
      <i class="fa-solid fa-check-double text-lg" aria-hidden="true"></i>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-5 text-center">
      <h2 id="unread-confirm-title" class="font-serif text-[1.85rem] font-semibold leading-[1.05] tracking-tight text-[#243746]">
        Marcar todo como leído
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-[1.6] text-gray-600">
        Todos los artículos pendientes desaparecerán de esta lista.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="mt-7 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:justify-center">
      <button
        type="button"
        class="inline-flex min-h-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full border border-[#D9D1C4] bg-white px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-[#3F3424] transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-[#F7F2E9]"
        data-unread-confirm-cancel
      >
        Cancelar
      </button>
      <button
        type="button"
        class="inline-flex min-h-12 items-center justify-center rounded-full bg-[#1F2937] px-5 py-3 text-sm font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.08em] text-white transition-colors duration-200 hover:bg-[#111827]"
        data-unread-confirm-accept
      >
        Sí, marcar todo
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</dialog>
